#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Launching &kfind;"
msgstr "Zagon &kfind;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Find Files tool is a useful method of searching for specific files on "
"your computer, or for searching for files that match a pattern. An example "
"of this could include searching for files of a particular type or with "
"certain letters in the filename. You can load this utility in &konqueror; "
"(in file manager mode) by selecting <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find File</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu. If "
"you want to use &kfind; as a standalone search tool, launch it by using "
"&krunner;."
msgstr ""
"Orodje za iskanje datotek je uporabna metoda za iskanje točno določenih "
"datotek na vašem računalniku ali pa za iskanje datotek, ki ustrezajo nekemu "
"vzorcu, na primer iskanje datotek določenega tipa ali z določenimi črkami v "
"imenu. Ta pripomoček si lahko naložite v &konqueror;-ju (v načinu "
"upravljalnika z datotekami), tako da izberete "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Najdi Datoteko</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz menija. Če želite uporabljati &kfind; kot "
"samostojno orodje za iskanje, ga poženite z &krunner;-jem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Files"
msgstr "Iskanje datotek"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Name/Location Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Ime/Mesto"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting &kfind;, you will see a quite simple window. Type in the name "
"of the file you are searching for in the text box labeled <guilabel>Named:</"
"guilabel>. You can use wildcard matching and a semicolon (<quote>;</quote>) "
"for separating multiple names."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &kfind;, se vam bo prikazalo precej preprosto okno. V besedilno "
"polje z oznako <guilabel>Ime:</guilabel> vpišite ime datoteke, ki jo iščete. "
"Lahko uporabite ujemanje nadomestnih znakov in podpičje (<quote>;</quote>), "
"da ločite več imen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose a folder where you want to search by typing it in the field "
"<guilabel>Look in:</guilabel> or by clicking <guibutton>Browse...</"
"guibutton> (you can toggle the display of the hidden files and folder in the "
"dialog using the shortcuts <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</"
"keycap></keycombo> or <keycap>F8</keycap>) and press &Enter; or click the "
"<guibutton>Find</guibutton> button. Use the <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> "
"button to cancel a search. A search result can be saved in &HTML; format or "
"as plain text with the <guibutton>Save As...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"V polje <guilabel>Išči v:</guilabel> vpišite ime mape, da izberete mesto, "
"kjer želite iskati. To lahko storite tudi s klikom na <guibutton>Prebrskaj..."
"</guibutton> (uporabite bljižnico <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</"
"keycap></keycombo> ali <keycap>F8</keycap>, da preklopite prikaz skritih "
"datotek in map), in nato pritisnite &Enter; ali kliknite na gumb "
"<guibutton>Najdi</guibutton>. Uporabite gumb <guibutton>Zaustavi</"
"guibutton>, da ustavite iskanje. Rezultat iskanja je mogoče shraniti v "
"formatu &HTML; ali kot navadno besedilo z gumbom <guibutton>Shrani kot...</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Include subfolders</guilabel> is checked all subfolders "
"starting from your chosen folder will be searched too. If you enable "
"<guilabel>Case sensitive search</guilabel>, &kfind; will only find files "
"with the exact case matching names. Enable the option <guilabel>Show hidden "
"files</guilabel> to include them in your search. Selecting <guilabel>Use "
"files index</guilabel> lets you use the files' index created by the "
"<quote>locate</quote> package to speed-up the search."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno polje <guilabel>Vključi podmape</guilabel>, bodo preiskane "
"tudi podmape, ki se nahajajo v izbrani mapi. Če omogočite način "
"<guilabel>Iskanje, občutljivo na velikost črk</guilabel>, bo &kfind; našel "
"le datoteke, katerih imena se natanko ujemajo z vpisanim. Omogočite možnost "
"<guilabel>Pokaži skrite datoteke</guilabel>, da jih vključite v svoje "
"iskanje. Če izberete <guilabel>Uporabi kazalo datoteke</guilabel>, lahko "
"uporabite kazalo datotek, ki ga je ustvaril <quote>locate</quote> paket, da "
"pohitrite iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can use the following wildcards for file or folder names:"
msgstr "Uporabite lahko naslednje nadomestne zanke v imenih datotek ali map:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Asterisk <quote><keycap>*</keycap></quote>"
msgstr "Zvezdica <quote><keycap>*</keycap></quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The asterisk stands for any number of missing characters (even zero), that "
"means &eg; searching for <userinput>marc*</userinput> may find the files "
"<filename>marc</filename>, <filename>marc.png</filename> and <filename> "
"marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>. <userinput>mar*.kwd</userinput> may "
"find <filename>marketplace.kwd</filename> and "
"<filename>marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Zvezdica predstavlja poljubno število manjkajočih znakov (tudi nič), kar "
"&eg; pomeni, da bo iskanje <filename>marc*</filename> vrnilo <filename>marc</"
"filename>, <filename>marc.png</filename> in <filename> "
"marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>. <filename>mar*.kwd</filename> pa bo "
"morda našel <filename>marketplace.kwd</filename> in "
"<filename>marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Question Mark <quote><keycap>?</keycap></quote>"
msgstr "Vprašaj <quote><keycap>?</keycap></quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In contrast to the asterisk, the question mark stands for exactly one "
"character, so <userinput>mar?</userinput> will find <filename>marc</"
"filename>, but <userinput>marc?</userinput> will not find anything, as our "
"files are called <filename>marc</filename> and <filename>marc.png</"
"filename>. You can put as many question marks in the term as you want, it "
"will find exactly that number of characters."
msgstr ""
"V nasprotju z zvezdico predstavlja vprašaj natanko en znak, tako da bo "
"<filename>mar?</filename> našel <filename>marc</filename>, medtem ko "
"<filename>marc?</filename> ne bo našel ničesar, saj se naše datoteke "
"imenujejo <filename>marc</filename> in <filename>marc.png</filename>. Dodate "
"lahko kolikor vprašaje želite, najdene bodo le datoteke, katerih ime ustreza "
"številu znakov."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Character Set <quote>[...]</quote>"
msgstr "Nabor Znakov <quote>[...]</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "This matches any of the characters between the braces."
msgstr "To se bo ujemalo s katerim koli znakom, ki je naveden v naboru."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course you can combine two or more wildcard symbols in a search term."
msgstr ""
"Seveda pa lahko v iskalnem izrazu poljubno kombinirate več nadomestnih "
"znakov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results of your search will be displayed in the box below. A click with "
"the &RMB; on a selection in this box opens a context menu with a list of "
"actions for the selected files or folders."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat vašega iskanja bo prikazan v spodnjem okvirčku. Z desnim klikom na "
"izbrane datoteke ali mape boste odprli meni s seznamom dejanj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Vsebina"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "File type"
msgstr "Vrsta datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can specify the type of file you are searching for."
msgstr "Tukaj lahko določite vrsto datoteke, ki jo iščete."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Containing text"
msgstr "Vsebuje besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type in the word or phrase the files you are searching for must contain. "
"Note: If you do this in a large folder or checked <guilabel>Include "
"subfolders</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Name/Location</guilabel> tab, this "
"may take a long time."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite besedo ali izraz, ki ga naj vsebuje datoteka, ki jo iščete. "
"Upoštevajte, da lahko iskanje, če to naredite v velikem imeniku ali pa "
"označite <guilabel>Vključi podmape</guilabel>, traja zelo dolgo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option will <emphasis>not</emphasis> work for all files listed under "
"<guilabel>File type</guilabel>. Only the following file types are supported:"
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost <emphasis>ne</emphasis> bo delovala za vse datoteke, ki so "
"navedene pod <guilabel>Vrsta datoteke</guilabel>. Podprte so samo naslednje "
"vrste datotek:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text files, &eg; source code and <filename>README</filename> files"
msgstr ""
"Besedilne datoteke, &eg; izvorna koda in datoteke <filename>README</filename>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Writer / LibreOffice Writer"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Writer / LibreOffice Writer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Impress / LibreOffice Impress"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Impress / LibreOffice Impress"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Calc / LibreOffice Calc"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Calc / LibreOffice Calc"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Words"
msgstr "Calligra Words"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Sheets"
msgstr "Calligra Sheets"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Stage"
msgstr "Calligra Stage"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Case sensitive"
msgstr "Iskanje občutljivo na velikost črk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable this option, &kfind; will only find text in files with the "
"exact case matching, &eg; <userinput>MARC</userinput> will only match "
"<quote>MARC</quote>, not <quote>Marc</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Če omogočite to možnost, bo &kfind; našel le besedila v datotekah, ki se "
"natanko ujemajo z vpisanim, na primer <userinput>MARC</userinput> se bo "
"ujemal le z <quote>MARC</quote> in ne z <quote>Marc</quote>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular expression"
msgstr "Uporabi ujemanje v regularnih izrazih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed the &kregexpeditor; tool from playground/utils on the "
"&kde; git server, you will have this additional option. Enabling it will "
"allow you to search for a <firstterm>regexp</firstterm> or regular "
"expression. A regexp is a way to specify conditions for your search, and "
"they can be very complex, and equally they can be very powerful. If you are "
"unfamiliar with regular expressions, you can choose <guibutton>Edit</"
"guibutton> button to open &kregexpeditor;. This tool allows you to construct "
"your set of conditions graphically, and then generates the expression for "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Če ste namestili orodje &kregexpeditor; iz playground/utils na &kde;-jevem "
"git strežniku, potem imate na voljo to dodatno možnost. Če bo omogočena, "
"boste lahko iskali <firstterm>regexp</firstterm> ali regularni izraz. "
"Regularni izrazi so način določevanja pogojev za vaše iskanje. So lahko zelo "
"zapleteni prav tako pa so tudi zelo zmogljivi. Če ne poznate regularnih "
"izrazov lahko izberete <guilabel>Uredi regularni izraz</guilabel>, da "
"odprete &kregexpeditor;. To orodje vam omogoča grafično načrtovanje množice "
"pogojev in nato ustvari izraz za vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kregexpeditor; is a very useful tool, and can be used from within many "
"&kde; applications other than &kfind;. You can find more information from "
"within its own help file."
msgstr ""
"&kregexpeditor; je zelo uporabno orodje in se lahko uporablja skupaj z "
"mnogimi programi &kde; poleg &kfind;. Več informacij o njem lahko najdete v "
"njegovi lastni datoteki s pomočjo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include binary files"
msgstr "Vključi binarne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lets you search in any type of file, even those that usually do not "
"contain text (for example program files and images)."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča iskanje v kateri koli datoteki, ne glede na vrsto, "
"celo v tistih, ki ponavadi ne vključujejo besedila, npr. programske datoteke "
"in slike."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search metainfo sections"
msgstr "Išči po metapodatkih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These two fields can be used to search within files' specific comments or "
"metainfo."
msgstr ""
"Ti dve polji sta namenjeni iskanju znotraj posebnih komentarjev ali "
"metapodatkov datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here are some major cases:"
msgstr "Tu je nekaj primerov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Video files (avi, mp4, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Bitrate</userinput>, <userinput>Duration</userinput>, &etc;) and "
"its value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Video datoteke (avi, mp4, &etc;)</emphasis>: navedite neko značko "
"(<userinput>Bitrate</userinput>, <userinput>Duration</userinput>, &etc;) in "
"njeno vrednost, da najdete datoteke s tem parametrom v svojih metapodatkih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Images (png, jpeg, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Width</userinput>, <userinput>Height</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Slike (png, jpeg, &etc;)</emphasis>: navedite neko značko "
"(<userinput>Width</userinput>, <userinput>Height</userinput>, &etc;) in "
"njeno vrednost, da najdete datoteke s tem parametrom v svojih metapodatkih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Audio files (mp3, flac, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Album</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Avdio datoteke (mp3, flac, &etc;)</emphasis>: navedite neko značko "
"(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Album</userinput>, &etc;) in njeno "
"vrednost, da najdete datoteke s tem parametrom v svojih metapodatkih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Ebooks (epub, azw, fb2, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Author</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Eknjige (epub, azw, fb2, &etc;)</emphasis>: navedite neko "
"značko(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Author</userinput>, &etc;) "
"in njeno vrednost, da najdete datoteke s tem parametrom v svojih "
"metapodatkih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is a translation of the tags into your language you can use the "
"localized tag names in the search criterion."
msgstr ""
"Če obstaja prevod teh značk v vašem jeziku, lahko pri iskanju uporabite "
"prevedena imena značk."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Properties Tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can refine your search. These are the special refinements you can "
"choose:"
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko izpopolnite svoje iskanje. Izbirate lahko med naslednjimi "
"izboljšavami:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find all files created or modified"
msgstr "Najdi vse datoteke, narejene ali spremenjene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can either enter two dates, between which the files were created or "
"modified, or specify a time period."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko vnesete dva datuma, med katerima je bila datoteka ustvarjena ali "
"spremenjena, ali pa navedete časovno obdobje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "File size is"
msgstr "Velikost je"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can specify if the file has to be at least or at most as big as the "
"size you entered in the following box, or else equal to the size."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko določite, ali mora biti datoteka vsaj, največ ali enako velika, kot "
"ste vnesli v sledeče polje."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Files owned by user</guilabel>, <guilabel>Files owned by group</"
"guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Lasti si jo uporabnik</guilabel>, <guilabel>Lasti si jo skupina</"
"guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can specify user and group names as owner of the files."
msgstr "Tu lahko navedete ime uporabnika ali skupine, ki so lastniki datotek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge in Licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kfind;"
msgstr "&kfind;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Program copyright:"
msgstr "Avtorske pravice (copyright):"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Developers"
msgstr "Razvijalci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "Martin Hartig"
msgstr "Martin Hartig"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Stephan.Kulow; &Stephan.Kulow.mail;"
